about.description:
A Python implementation of Jacquez's Q statistics for space-time clustering
of disease exposure in case-control studies.
about.summary: Open Soure Jacquez's Q-Statistics for Space-Time Clustering

name: jacqq
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "JacqQ" %}
{% set version = "0.5.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/sjirjies/py{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6997311506185504d71d28ccac22889bfef230bb146c4907dff5f61357c1b31b

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.4
  run:
    - python >=3.4
    - scipy
    - numpy

test:
  imports:
    - jacqq

about:
  home: https://github.com/sjirjies/pyJacqQ
  license: GPL-3
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Open Soure Jacquez's Q-Statistics for Space-Time Clustering"
  description: |
    A Python implementation of Jacquez's Q statistics for space-time clustering
    of disease exposure in case-control studies.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - benhuff
    - rluria14
    - oblute
